<link=\"ATMOSUIT\">Atmo Suits</link> can be equipped to protect my Duplicants from environmental hazards like extreme <link=\"HEAT\">Heat</link>, airborne <link=\"DISEASE\">Germs</link>, or unbreathable <link=\"ELEMENTSGAS\">Gas</link>. In order to utilize these suits, I'll need to hook up an <link=\"SUITLOCKER\">Atmo Suit Dock</link> to an <link=\"SUITMARKER\">Atmo Suit Checkpoint</link> , then store one of the suits inside.\n\nDuplicants will equip a suit when they walk past the checkpoint in the chosen direction, and will unequip their suit when walking back the opposite way.